description: The Intel 10th Gen Core i3 10100T Processor is a low-power quad-core processor designed for efficient computing. With a base clock of 3.0GHz and a max turbo boost speed of 3.8GHz, it provides a balance of performance and power efficiency. It features 6MB of L3 cache and supports DDR4 memory at 2666MHz.

The Intel 11th Gen Core i7 11700K Processor is a high-performance processor for gaming and content creation. It features 8 cores and 16 threads, a base clock of 3.6GHz, and a max turbo frequency of 5.0GHz. With 16MB of L3 cache and support for DDR4 memory at 3200MHz, it delivers exceptional performance.

The Intel 9th Gen Core i5 9600K Processor is a popular choice for gamers and enthusiasts. It features 6 cores and 6 threads, a base clock of 3.7GHz, and a max turbo frequency of 4.6GHz. With 9MB of L3 cache and support for DDR4 memory at 2666MHz, it delivers solid gaming performance.
